title: Android app is not responsive when recovering account having chat with message
body:

*Type*: Bug

*Summary*: cant navigate through tabs for some time when I log in to the recovered account which has chat with add to contacts request


#### Actual behavior
App is not usable for some time (5-6 min) then it could be used

### Reproduction

- Open Status
- Recover account which has chat with add to contacts request


### Additional Information
* Status version: nightly June 4
* Operating System: Android
